Title: Linde Werdelin SPIDOLITE GOLD - 18k Rose Gold Watch
Description: LINDE WERDILINE SPIDOLITE GOLD Limited to 75 individually numbered pieces worldwide this is a amazing collectors piece and a true work or art. DESCRIPTION Extremely rare as only 75 will ever be produced. 18k Rose Gold brushed case, pushers, screws and a polished and brushed bezel. Skeletonized dial with chronograph function truly a work of art. Comes complete with inner & outer box, digital owner manual, LW owners card and LW polishing cloth. OVERVIEW Dexterity in skeletonised design, the SpidoLite Gold proves 18K rose gold can produce an agile timepiece.The SpidoLite Gold, the fourth generation of the SpidoLite family, marks an evolution in weight-optimised construction and reveals the first ever Linde Werdelin power reserve indicator.
